abomasnow.dex_entry: It whips up blizzards in mountains that are always buried in snow. It is the abominable snowman.
abomasnow.name: abomasnow

abra.dex_entry: A Pokémon that sleeps 18 hours a day. Observation revealed that it uses Teleport to change its location once every hour.
abra.name: abra

absol.dex_entry: It sharply senses even subtle changes in the sky and the land to predict natural disasters. It is a long-lived Pokémon that has a life-span of 100 years.
absol.name: absol

accelgor.dex_entry: Having removed its heavy shell, it becomes very light and can fight with ninja-like movements.
accelgor.name: accelgor

aegislash.dex_entry: Apparently, it can detect the innate qualities of leadership. According to legend, whoever it recognizes is destined to become king.
aegislash.name: aegislash

aerodactyl.dex_entry: Aerodactyl is a Pokémon from the age of dinosaurs. It was regenerated from DNA extracted from amber. It is imagined to have been the king of the skies.
aerodactyl.name: aerodactyl

aggron.dex_entry: Its iron horns grow longer a little at a time. They are used to determine the Aggron's age. The gouges in its armor are worn with pride as mementos from battles.
aggron.name: aggron

aipom.dex_entry: Its tail ends with a dexterous, handlike appendage. However, because it uses the tail so much, Aipom's real hands have become rather clumsy.
aipom.name: aipom

alakazam.dex_entry: While it has strong psychic abilities and high intelligence, an Alakazam's muscles are very weak. It uses psychic power to move its body.
alakazam.name: alakazam

alomomola.dex_entry: Floating in the open sea is how they live. When they find a wounded Pokémon, they embrace it and bring it to shore.
alomomola.name: alomomola

altaria.dex_entry: It hums in a beautiful soprano voice. It flies among white clouds in the blue sky. It launches intensely hot fireballs from its mouth.
altaria.name: altaria

amaura.dex_entry: This ancient Pokemon was restored from part of its body that had been frozen in ice for over 100 million years.
amaura.name: amaura

ambipom.dex_entry: To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now.
ambipom.name: ambipom

amoonguss.dex_entry: They show off their Poké Ball caps to lure prey, but very few Pokémon are fooled by this.
amoonguss.name: amoonguss

ampharos.dex_entry: It gives off so much light that it can be seen even from space. People in the old days used its light to send signals back and forth with others far away.
ampharos.name: ampharos

anorith.dex_entry: It was resurrected from a fossil using the power of science. It swims by undulating the eight wings at its sides. They were feet that adapted to life in the sea.
anorith.name: anorith

araquanid.dex_entry: It delivers headbutts with the water bubbleon its head. Small Pokémon get sucked in the bubble and drown.
araquanid.name: araquanid

arbok.dex_entry: This Pokémon has a terrifically strong constricting power. It can even flatten steel oil drums. Once it wraps its body around its foe, escaping is impossible.
arbok.name: arbok

arcanine.dex_entry: This fleet-footed Pokémon is said to run over 6,200 miles in a single day and night. The fire that blazes wildly within its body is its source of power.
arcanine.name: arcanine

arceus.dex_entry: It is described in mythology as the Pokémon that shaped the universe with its 1,000 arms.
arceus.name: arceus

archen.dex_entry: Revived from a fossil, this Pokémon is thought to be the ancestor of all bird Pokémon.
archen.name: archen

archeops.dex_entry: It runs better than it flies. It catches prey by running at speeds comparable to those of an automobile.
archeops.name: archeops

ariados.dex_entry: Its feet are tipped with tiny hooked claws that enable it to scuttle on ceilings and vertical walls. It constricts its foe with thin and strong silk webbing.
ariados.name: ariados

armaldo.dex_entry: Armaldo usually lives on land. However, when it hunts for prey, it dives beneath the ocean. It swims around using its two large wings.
armaldo.name: armaldo

aromatisse.dex_entry: Its scent is so overpowering that, unless a Trainer happens to really enjoy the smell, he or she will have a hard time walking alongside it.
aromatisse.name: aromatisse

aron.dex_entry: A Pokémon that is clad in steel armor. A new suit of armor is made when it evolves. The old, discarded armor is salvaged as metal for making iron products.
aron.name: aron

articuno.dex_entry: Articuno is a legendary bird Pokémon that can control ice. The flapping of its wings chills the air. As a result, it is said that when this Pokémon flies, snow will fall.
articuno.name: articuno

audino.dex_entry: Its auditory sense is astounding. It has a radar-like ability to understand its surrounding through slight sounds.
audino.name: audino

aurorus.dex_entry: The diamond-shaped crystals on its body expel air as cold as -240 degrees Fahrenheit, surrounding its enemies and encasing them in ice.
aurorus.name: aurorus

avalugg.dex_entry: Its ice-covered body is as hard as steel. Its cumbersome frame crushes anything that stands in its way.
avalugg.name: avalugg

axew.dex_entry: They mark their territory by leaving gashes in trees with their tusks. If a tusk breaks, a new one grows in quickly.
axew.name: axew

azelf.dex_entry: Known as ΓÇ£The Being of Willpower.ΓÇ¥ It sleeps at the bottom of a lake to keep the world in balance.
azelf.name: azelf

azumarill.dex_entry: It lives in water virtually all day long. Its body color and pattern act as camouflage that makes it tough for enemies to spot in water.
azumarill.name: azumarill

azurill.dex_entry: Its tail, which is packed with nutrition, is very bouncy like a rubber ball. On sunny days they gather at the edge of water and splash about for fun.
azurill.name: azurill

bagon.dex_entry: Although it is small, this Pokémon is very powerful because its body is a bundle of muscles. It launches head-butts with its ironlike skull.
bagon.name: bagon

baltoy.dex_entry: A Baltoy moves by spinning on its single foot. It has been depicted in murals adorning the walls of a once-bustling city in an ancient age.
baltoy.name: baltoy

banette.dex_entry: An abandoned plush doll became this Pokémon. They are said to live in garbage dumps and wander about in search of the children that threw them away.
banette.name: banette

barbaracle.dex_entry: Barbaracle's legs and hands have minds of their own, and they will move independently. But they usually follow the head's orders.
barbaracle.name: barbaracle

barboach.dex_entry: Its body is covered with a slimy film. The film acts as a barrier to prevent germs in muddy water from entering the Barboach's body.
barboach.name: barboach

basculin.dex_entry: Red and blue Basculin usually do not get along, but sometimes members of one school mingle with the other's schooL.
basculin.name: basculin

bastiodon.dex_entry: Any frontal attack is repulsed. It is a docile Pokémon that feeds on grass and berries.
bastiodon.name: bastiodon

bayleef.dex_entry: A Bayleef's neck is ringed by curled-up leaves. Inside each leaf is a small tree shoot. The fragrance of this shoot makes people peppy.
bayleef.name: bayleef

beartic.dex_entry: It freezes its breath to create fangs and claws of ice to fight with. Cold northern areas are its habitat.
beartic.name: beartic

beautifly.dex_entry: Its colorfully patterned wings are its most prominent feature. It flies through flower-covered fields collecting pollen. It attacks ferociously when angered.
beautifly.name: beautifly

beedrill.dex_entry: A Beedrill is extremely territorial. For safety reasons, no one should ever approach its nest. If angered, they will attack in a swarm.
beedrill.name: beedrill

beheeyem.dex_entry: It uses psychic power to control an opponent's brain and tamper with its memories.
beheeyem.name: beheeyem

beldum.dex_entry: When Beldum gather in a swarm, they move in perfect unison as if they were but one Pokémon. They communicate with each other using brain waves.
beldum.name: beldum

bellossom.dex_entry: Its flower petals deepen in color through exposure to sunlight. When cloudy weather persists, it does a dance that is thought to be a ritual for summoning the sun.
bellossom.name: bellossom

bellsprout.dex_entry: A Bellsprout's thin and flexible body lets it bend and sway to avoid any attack, however strong it may be. From its mouth, it leaks a fluid that melts even iron.
bellsprout.name: bellsprout

bergmite.dex_entry: It blocks opponents' attacks with the ice that shields its body. It uses cold air to repair any cracks with new ice.
bergmite.name: bergmite

bewear.dex_entry: This immensely dangerous Pokémon possesses overwhelming strength. Its habitat is generally off=limits.
bewear.name: bewear

bibarel.dex_entry: It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.
bibarel.name: bibarel

bidoof.dex_entry: With nerves of steel, nothing can perturb it. It is more agile and active than it appears.
bidoof.name: bidoof

binacle.dex_entry: Two Binacle live together on one rock. When they fight, one of them will move to a different rock.
binacle.name: binacle

bisharp.dex_entry: Bisharp pursues prey in the company of a large group of Pawniard. Then Bisharp finishes off the prey.
bisharp.name: bisharp

blastoise.dex_entry: The waterspouts that protrude from its shell are highly accurate. Their bullets of water can precisely nail tin cans from a distance of over 160 feet.
blastoise.name: blastoise

blaziken.dex_entry: It learns martial arts that use punches and kicks. Every several years, its old feathers burn off, and new, supple feathers grow back in their place.
blaziken.name: blaziken

blissey.dex_entry: If it senses sadness with its fluffy fur, a Blissey will rush over to the sad person, however far away, to share an egg of happiness that brings a smile to any face.
blissey.name: blissey

blitzle.dex_entry: When thunderclouds cover the sky, it will appear. It can catch lightning with its mane and store the electricity.
blitzle.name: blitzle

boldore.dex_entry: Because its energy was too great to be contained, the energy leaked and formed orange crystals.
boldore.name: boldore

bonsly.dex_entry: It looks as if it is always crying. It is actually adjusting its body's fluid levels by eliminating excess.
bonsly.name: bonsly

bouffalant.dex_entry: They charge wildly and headbutt everything. They headbutts have enough destructive force to derail a train.
bouffalant.name: bouffalant

bounsweet.dex_entry: A delectable aroma pours from its body. They are often swallowed by birds lured by that wafting deliciousness.
bounsweet.name: bounsweet

braixen.dex_entry: When the twig is plucked from its tail, friction sets the twig alight. The flame is used to send signals to its allies.
braixen.name: braixen

braviary.dex_entry: The more scars they have, the more respect these brave soldiers of the sky get from their peers.
braviary.name: braviary

breloom.dex_entry: It scatters spores from holes in the cap on its head. It loves warm and humid climates. It feeds on trees and plants in fields and forests.
breloom.name: breloom

brionne.dex_entry: A skillful dancer, it creates a sequence of water balloons as it dances, and briskly bombards its enemies.
brionne.name: brionne

bronzong.dex_entry: One caused a news sensation when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2,000-year sleep.
bronzong.name: bronzong

bronzor.dex_entry: Implements shaped like it were discovered in ancient tombs. It is unknown if they are related.
bronzor.name: bronzor

bruxish.dex_entry: It stuns its prey with psychokinesis and then grinds them to mush with its strong teeth.
bruxish.name: bruxish

budew.dex_entry: Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.
budew.name: budew

buizel.dex_entry: It has a flotation sac that is like an inflatable collar. It floats on water with its head out.
buizel.name: buizel

bulbasaur.dex_entry: Bulbasaur can be seen napping in bright sunlight. There is a seed on its back. By soaking up the sun's rays, the seed grows progressively larger.
bulbasaur.name: bulbasaur

buneary.dex_entry: It slams foes by sharply uncoiling its rolled ears. It stings enough to make a grown-up cry in pain.
buneary.name: buneary

bunnelby.dex_entry: It has ears like shovels. Digging holes strengthens its ears so much that they can sever thick roots effortlessly.
bunnelby.name: bunnelby

burmy.dex_entry: To shelter itself from cold, wintry winds, it covers itself with a cloak made of twigs and leaves.
burmy.name: burmy

butterfree.dex_entry: It has a superior ability to search for delicious honey from flowers. It can seek, extract, and carry honey from flowers blooming over six miles away.
butterfree.name: butterfree

buzzwole.dex_entry: People saw it pulverize a dump truck with a single punch. It is an Ultra Beast.
buzzwole.name: buzzwole

cacnea.dex_entry: Cacnea live in deserts with virtually no rainfall. It battles by swinging its thick, spiked arms. Once a year, a yellow flower blooms.
cacnea.name: cacnea

cacturne.dex_entry: After spending thousands of years in harsh deserts, its blood transformed into the same substances as sand. It is nocturnal, so it hunts at night.
cacturne.name: cacturne

camerupt.dex_entry: A Pokémon that lives in the crater of a volcano. Every 10 years, the volcanoes on its back erupt violently. Research is under way on the cause of eruption.
camerupt.name: camerupt

carbink.dex_entry: It has slept underground for hundreds of millions of years since its birth. It's occasionally found during the excavation of caves.
carbink.name: carbink

carnivine.dex_entry: It attracts prey with its sweet-smelling saliva, then chomps down. It takes a whole day to eat prey.
carnivine.name: carnivine

carracosta.dex_entry: Incredible jaw strength enables them to chew up steel beams and rocks along with their prey.
carracosta.name: carracosta

carvanha.dex_entry: Carvanha attack ships in swarms, making them sink. Although it is said to be a very vicious Pokémon, it timidly flees as soon as it finds itself alone.
carvanha.name: carvanha

cascoon.dex_entry: To avoid detection by its enemies, it hides motionlessly beneath large leaves and in the gaps of branches. It also attaches dead leaves to its body for camouflage.
cascoon.name: cascoon

castform.dex_entry: It alters its form depending on the weather. Changes in the climate such as the temperature and humidity appear to affect its cellular structure.
castform.name: castform

caterpie.dex_entry: Its voracious appetite compels it to devour leaves bigger than itself without hesitation. It releases a terribly strong odor from its antennae.
caterpie.name: caterpie

celebi.dex_entry: This Pokémon came from the future by crossing over time. It is thought that so long as Celebi appears, a bright and shining future awaits us.
celebi.name: celebi

celesteela.dex_entry: People have seen it burn down a forest by expelling gas from its two arms. It is an Ultra Beast.
celesteela.name: celesteela

chandelure.dex_entry: Being consumed in Chandelure's flame burns up the spirit, leaving the body behind.
chandelure.name: chandelure

chansey.dex_entry: Chansey lay nutritionally excellent eggs every day. The eggs are so delicious, they are eagerly devoured by even those who have lost their appetite.
chansey.name: chansey

charizard.dex_entry: A Charizard flies about in search of strong opponents. It breathes intense flames that can melt any material. However, it will never torch a weaker foe.
charizard.name: charizard

charjabug.dex_entry: Its body is capable of storing electricity. On camping trips, people are grateful to have one around.
charjabug.name: charjabug

charmander.dex_entry: The flame that burns at the tip of its tail is an indication of its emotions. The flame wavers when Charmander is happy, and blazes when it is enraged.
charmander.name: charmander

charmeleon.dex_entry: Without pity, its sharp claws destroy foes. If it encounters a strong enemy, it becomes agitated, and the flame on its tail flares with a bluish white color.
charmeleon.name: charmeleon

chatot.dex_entry: It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.
chatot.name: chatot

cherrim.dex_entry: It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud.
cherrim.name: cherrim

cherubi.dex_entry: The small ball holds the nutrients needed for evolution. Apparently, it is very sweet and tasty.
cherubi.name: cherubi

chesnaught.dex_entry: When it takes a defensive posture with its fists guarding its face, it could withstand a bomb blast.
chesnaught.name: chesnaught

chespin.dex_entry: The quills on its head are usually soft. When it flexes them, the points become so hard and sharp that they can pierce rock.
chespin.name: chespin

chikorita.dex_entry: It waves its leaf around to keep foes at bay. However, a sweet fragrance also wafts from the leaf, creating a friendly atmosphere that becalms the battlers.
chikorita.name: chikorita

chimchar.dex_entry: It agilely scales sheer cliffs to live atop craggy mountains. Its fire is put out when it sleeps.
chimchar.name: chimchar

chimecho.dex_entry: They fly about very actively when the hot season arrives. They communicate among themselves using seven different and distinguishing cries.
chimecho.name: chimecho

chinchou.dex_entry: When it senses danger, it discharges positive and negative electricity from its two antennae. It lives in depths beyond sunlight's reach.
chinchou.name: chinchou

chingling.dex_entry: It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.
chingling.name: chingling

cinccino.dex_entry: Their white fur feels amazing to touch. Their fur repels dust and prevents static electricity from building up.
cinccino.name: cinccino

clamperl.dex_entry: A Clamperl slams its shell closed on prey to prevent escape. The pearl it creates upon evolution is said to be infused with a mysterious energy.
clamperl.name: clamperl

clauncher.dex_entry: They knock down flying prey by firing compressed water from their massive claws like shooting a pistol.
clauncher.name: clauncher

clawitzer.dex_entry: Their enormous claws launch cannonballs of water powerful enough to pierce tanker hulls.
clawitzer.name: clawitzer

claydol.dex_entry: A Claydol sleeps while hovering in midair. Its arms are separate from its body. They are kept floating by the Pokémon's manipulation of psychic power.
claydol.name: claydol

clefable.dex_entry: A Clefable uses its wings to skip lightly as if it were flying. Its bouncy step lets it even walk on water. On quiet, moonlit nights, it strolls on lakes.
clefable.name: clefable

clefairy.dex_entry: On every night of a full moon, they come out to play. When dawn arrives, the tired Clefairy go to sleep nestled up against each other in deep and quiet mountains.
clefairy.name: clefairy

cleffa.dex_entry: On nights with many shooting stars, Cleffa can be seen dancing in a ring. They dance until daybreak, when they quench their thirst with the morning dew.
cleffa.name: cleffa

cloyster.dex_entry: It swims in the sea by swallowing water, then jetting it out toward the rear. The Cloyster shoots spikes from its shell using the same system.
cloyster.name: cloyster

cobalion.dex_entry: It has a body and heart of steel. Its glare is sufficient to make even an unruly Pokémon obey it.
cobalion.name: cobalion

cofagrigus.dex_entry: They pretend to be elaborate coffins to teach lessons to grave robbers. Their bodies are covered in pure gold.
cofagrigus.name: cofagrigus

combee.dex_entry: A Pokémon formed by three others. It busily carries sweet floral honey to Vespiquen.
combee.name: combee

combusken.dex_entry: It lashes out with 10 kicks per second. Its strong fighting instinct compels it to keep up its offensive until the opponent gives up.
combusken.name: combusken

comfey.dex_entry: It attaches flowers to its highly nutritious vine. This revitalizes the flower and give off an aromatic scent.
comfey.name: comfey

conkeldurr.dex_entry: They use concrete pillars as walking canes. They know moves that enable them to swing the pillars freely in battle.
conkeldurr.name: conkeldurr

corphish.dex_entry: Once it grips prey with its large pincers, it will never let go, no matter what. It is a hardy Pokémon that can thrive in any environment.
corphish.name: corphish

corsola.dex_entry: Corsola live in warm southern seas. If the sea becomes polluted, the beautiful coral stalks become discolored and crumble away in tatters.
corsola.name: corsola

cosmoem.dex_entry: Motionless as if dead, its body is faintly warm to the touch. In the distant past, it was called the cocoon of stars.
cosmoem.name: cosmoem

cosmog.dex_entry: Its body is gaseous and frail. It slowsly grows as it collects dust from the atmosphere.
cosmog.name: cosmog

cottonee.dex_entry: They go wherever the wind takes them. On rainy days, their bodies are heavier, so they take shelter beneath big trees.
cottonee.name: cottonee

crabominable.dex_entry: It aimed for the top but got lost and ended up on a snowy mountain. Being forced to endure the cold, this Pokémon evolved.
crabominable.name: crabominable

crabrawler.dex_entry: It punches so much, its pincers often come off from overuse, but they grow back quickly.
crabrawler.name: crabrawler

cradily.dex_entry: It drags its heavy body along the seafloor. It makes its nest in the shallows of warm seas. Cradily can be seen on beaches when the tide goes out.
cradily.name: cradily

cranidos.dex_entry: It lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its skull is as hard as iron.
cranidos.name: cranidos

crawdaunt.dex_entry: A brutish Pokémon that loves to battle. A veteran Crawdaunt that has prevailed in hundreds of battles has giant pincers marked with countless scars.
crawdaunt.name: crawdaunt

cresselia.dex_entry: Shiny particles are released from its wings like a veil. It is said to represent the crescent moon.
cresselia.name: cresselia

croagunk.dex_entry: Its cheeks hold poison sacs. It tries to catch foes off guard to jab them with toxic fingers.
croagunk.name: croagunk

crobat.dex_entry: Over the course of evolution, its hind legs turned into wings. By alternately resting its front and rear wings, it can fly all day without having to stop.
crobat.name: crobat

croconaw.dex_entry: Once its jaws clamp down on its foe, it will absolutely not let go. Because the tips of its fangs are forked back like fishhooks, they become irremovably embedded.
croconaw.name: croconaw

crustle.dex_entry: It possesses legs of enormous strength, enabling it to carry heavy slabs for many days, even when crossing arid land.
crustle.name: crustle

cryogonal.dex_entry: They are born in snow clouds. They use chains made of ice crystals to capture prey.
cryogonal.name: cryogonal

cubchoo.dex_entry: Its nose is always running. It sniffs the snot back up because the mucus provides the raw material for its moves.
cubchoo.name: cubchoo

cubone.dex_entry: It pines for the mother it will never see again. Seeing a likeness of its mother in the full moon, it cries. The stains on the skull it wears are from its tears.
cubone.name: cubone

cutiefly.dex_entry: Because Cutiefly are able to sense auras, they can identify which flowers are about to bloom.
cutiefly.name: cutiefly

cyndaquil.dex_entry: It flares flames from its back to protect itself. The fire burns vigorously if the Pokémon is angry. When it is tired, it sputters with incomplete combustion.
cyndaquil.name: cyndaquil

darkrai.dex_entry: It can lull people to sleep and make them dream. It is active during nights of the new moon.
darkrai.name: darkrai

darmanitan.dex_entry: When weakened in battle, it transforms into a stone statue. Then it sharpens its mind and fights on mentally.
darmanitan.name: darmanitan

dartrix.dex_entry: It spends its free time preening its wings. Its preoccupation with any dirt on its plumage can leave it unable to battle.
dartrix.name: dartrix

darumaka.dex_entry: Darumaka's droppings are hot, so people used to put them in their clothes to keep themselves warm.
darumaka.name: darumaka

decidueye.dex_entry: It fires arrow quills from its wings with such precision, they can pierce a pebble from over hundred yards.
decidueye.name: decidueye

dedenne.dex_entry: It uses its tail to absorb electricity from power plants or from outlets in houses, and then it fires the electricity from its whiskers.
dedenne.name: dedenne

deerling.dex_entry: The turning of the seasons changes the color and scent of this Pokémon's fur. People use it to mark the seasons.
deerling.name: deerling

deino.dex_entry: They cannot see, so they tackle and bite to learn about their surroundings. Their bodies are covered in wounds.
deino.name: deino

delcatty.dex_entry: Rather than keeping a permanent lair, it habitually seeks comfortable spots and sleeps there. It is nocturnal and becomes active at dusk.
delcatty.name: delcatty

delibird.dex_entry: It carries food bundled up in its tail. There was a famous explorer who managed to scale Mt. Everest thanks to a Delibird sharing its food.
delibird.name: delibird

delphox.dex_entry: It gazes into the flame at the tip of its branch to achieve a focused state, which allows it to see into the future.
delphox.name: delphox

deoxys.dex_entry: A Pokémon that mutated from an extraterrestrial virus exposed to a laser beam. Its body is configured for superior agility and speed.
deoxys.name: deoxys

dewgong.dex_entry: It loves to snooze on bitterly cold ice. The sight of this Pokémon sleeping on a glacier was mistakenly thought to be a mermaid by a mariner long ago.
dewgong.name: dewgong

dewott.dex_entry: Scalchop techniques differ from one Dewott to another. It never neglects maintaining its scalchops.
dewott.name: dewott

dewpider.dex_entry: It crawls onto the land in search of food. Its water bubble allows it to breathe and protects its soft head.
dewpider.name: dewpider

dhelmise.dex_entry: Swinging its massive anchor, it can KO Wailord in a single blow. What appears to be green seaweed is actually its body.
dhelmise.name: dhelmise

dialga.dex_entry: It has the power to control time. It appears in Sinnoh-region myths as an ancient deity.
dialga.name: dialga

diancie.dex_entry: A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.
diancie.name: diancie

diggersby.dex_entry: As powerful as an excavator, its ears can reduce dense bedrock to rubble. When itΓÇÖs finished digging, it lounges lazily.
diggersby.name: diggersby

diglett.dex_entry: Diglett are raised in most farms. The reason is simple--wherever they burrow, the soil is left perfectly tilled for growing delicious crops.
diglett.name: diglett

diglett-alola.dex_entry: Its golden hairs function as sensors. It pokes them out of its burrow to monitor its surroundings.
diglett-alola.name: diglett-alola

ditto.dex_entry: A Ditto rearranges its cell structure to transform itself. However, if it tries to change based on its memory, it will get details wrong.
ditto.name: ditto

dodrio.dex_entry: A peculiar Pokémon species with three heads. It vigorously races across grassy plains even in arid seasons with little rainfall.
dodrio.name: dodrio

doduo.dex_entry: Even while eating or sleeping, one of the heads remains always vigilant for any sign of danger. When threatened, it flees at over 60 miles per hour.
doduo.name: doduo

donphan.dex_entry: A Donphan is so strong it can easily haul a dump truck. Its hide has toughened to a rock-hard state. An ordinary sort of attack won't even leave a scratch.
donphan.name: donphan

doublade.dex_entry: The complex attack patterns of its two swords are unstoppable, even for an opponent greatly accomplished at swordplay.
doublade.name: doublade

dragalge.dex_entry: Tales are told of ships that wander into seas where Dragalge live, never to return.
dragalge.name: dragalge

dragonair.dex_entry: A Dragonair stores an enormous amount of energy inside its body. It is said to alter the weather around it by loosing energy from the crystals on its neck and tail.
dragonair.name: dragonair

dragonite.dex_entry: It can circle the globe in just 16 hours. It is a kindhearted Pokémon that leads lost and foundering ships in a storm to the safety of land.
dragonite.name: dragonite

drampa.dex_entry: It has a compassionate personality, but when angered, it completely destroys its surroundings with its breath.
drampa.name: drampa

drapion.dex_entry: It has the power in its clawed arms to make scrap of a car. The tips of its claws release poison.
drapion.name: drapion

dratini.dex_entry: A Dratini continually molts and sloughs off its old skin. It does so because the life energy within its body steadily builds to reach uncontrollable levels.
dratini.name: dratini

drifblim.dex_entry: It's drowzy in daytime, but flies off in the evening in big groups. No one knows where they go.
drifblim.name: drifblim

drifloon.dex_entry: A Pokémon formed by the spirits of people and Pokémon. It loves damp, humid seasons.
drifloon.name: drifloon

drilbur.dex_entry: It makes its way swiftly through the soil by putting both claws together and rotating at high speed.
drilbur.name: drilbur

drowzee.dex_entry: If your nose becomes itchy while you are sleeping, it's a sure sign that a Drowzee is standing above your pillow and trying to eat your dream through your nostrils.
drowzee.name: drowzee

druddigon.dex_entry: It races through narrow caves, using its sharp claws to catch prey. Then skin on its face is harder than a rock.
druddigon.name: druddigon

ducklett.dex_entry: When attacked, it uses its feathers to splash water, escaping under cover of the spray.
ducklett.name: ducklett

dugtrio.dex_entry: Because the triplets originally split from one body, they think exactly alike. They work cooperatively to burrow endlessly through the ground.
dugtrio.name: dugtrio

dugtrio-alola.dex_entry: Its shining gold hair provides it with protection. It's reputed that keeping any of its fallen hairs will bring bad luck.
dugtrio-alola.name: dugtrio-alola

dunsparce.dex_entry: Its drill-tipped tail is used to burrow into the ground backwards. This Pokémon is known to make its nest in complex shapes deep under the ground.
dunsparce.name: dunsparce

duosion.dex_entry: When their brains, now divided in two, are thinking the same thoughts, these Pokémon exhibit their maximum power.
duosion.name: duosion

durant.dex_entry: Durant dig nests in mountains. They build their complicated, interconnected tunnels in mazes.
durant.name: durant

dusclops.dex_entry: It is thought that its body is hollow with only a spectral ball of fire burning inside. However, no one has been able to confirm this theory as fact.
dusclops.name: dusclops

dusknoir.dex_entry: The antenna on its head captures radio waves from the world of spirits that command it to take people there.
dusknoir.name: dusknoir

duskull.dex_entry: A glare from its single scarlet eye makes even burly grown-ups freeze in utter fear. It is a nocturnal Pokémon that roams about under the cloak of darkness.
duskull.name: duskull

dustox.dex_entry: It is a nocturnal Pokémon that flies from fields and mountains to the attraction of streetlights at night. It looses highly toxic powder from its wings.
dustox.name: dustox

dwebble.dex_entry: It makes a hole in a suitable rock. If that rock breaks, the Pokémon remains agitated until it locates a replacement.
dwebble.name: dwebble

eelektrik.dex_entry: These Pokémon have a big appetite. When they spot their prey, they attack it and paralyze it with electricity.
eelektrik.name: eelektrik

eelektross.dex_entry: With their sucker mouths, they suck in prey. Then they use their fangs to shock the prey with electricity.
eelektross.name: eelektross

eevee.dex_entry: An Eevee has an unstable genetic makeup that suddenly mutates due to its environment. Radiation from various stones causes this Pokémon to evolve.
eevee.name: eevee

ekans.dex_entry: An Ekans curls itself up in a spiral while it rests. This position allows it to quickly respond to an enemy from any direction with a threat from its upraised head.
ekans.name: ekans

electabuzz.dex_entry: When a storm approaches, it competes with others to scale heights that are likely to be stricken by lightning. Some towns use Electabuzz in place of lightning rods.
electabuzz.name: electabuzz

electivire.dex_entry: It pushes the tips of its two tails against the foe, then lets loose with over 20,000 volts of power.
electivire.name: electivire

electrike.dex_entry: It generates electricity using friction from the atmosphere. In seasons with especially arid air, its entire body blazes with violent showers of sparks.
electrike.name: electrike

electrode.dex_entry: They appear in great numbers at electric power plants. Because they feed on electricity, they cause massive and chaotic blackouts in nearby cities.
electrode.name: electrode

elekid.dex_entry: If it touches metal and discharges the electricity it has stored in its body, an Elekid begins swinging its arms in circles to recharge itself.
elekid.name: elekid

elgyem.dex_entry: This Pokémon had never been seen until it appeared from far in the desert 50 years ago.
elgyem.name: elgyem

emboar.dex_entry: It can throw a fire punch by setting its fists on fire with its fiery chin. It cares deeply about its friends.
emboar.name: emboar

emolga.dex_entry: They live on treetops and glide using the inside of a cape-like membrane while discharging electricity.
emolga.name: emolga

empoleon.dex_entry: The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.
empoleon.name: empoleon

entei.dex_entry: Entei embodies the passion of magma. It is thought to have been born in the eruption of a volcano. It blasts fire that consumes all that it touches.
entei.name: entei

escavalier.dex_entry: These Pokémon evolve by wearing the shell covering of a Shelmet. The steel armor protects their whole body.
escavalier.name: escavalier

espeon.dex_entry: An Espeon is extremely loyal to any trainer it considers to be worthy. It is said to have developed precognitive powers to protect its trainer from harm.
espeon.name: espeon

espurr.dex_entry: It has enough psychic energy to blast everything within 300 feet of itself, but it has no control over its power.
espurr.name: espurr

excadrill.dex_entry: More than 300 feet below the surface, they build mazelike nests. Their activity can be destructive to subway tunnels.
excadrill.name: excadrill

exeggcute.dex_entry: It consists of six eggs that care for each other. The eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear, it is close to evolution.
exeggcute.name: exeggcute

exeggutor.dex_entry: Originally from the tropics, Exeggutor's heads grow larger from exposure to strong sunlight. It is said that when the heads fall, they group to form an Exeggcute.
exeggutor.name: exeggutor

exeggutor-alola.dex_entry: As it grew taller and taller, it outgrew its reliance on psychic powers, awakening the power of the sleeping dragon.
exeggutor-alola.name: exeggutor-alola

exploud.dex_entry: It has sound-generating organs all over its body. It communicates with others by adjusting the tone and volume of the cries it emits.
exploud.name: exploud

farfetch'd.dex_entry: It is always seen with a stick from a plant. Apparently, there are good sticks and bad sticks. This Pokémon occasionally fights with others over choice sticks.
farfetch'd.name: farfetch'd

fearow.dex_entry: Its long neck and elongated beak are ideal for catching prey in soil or water. It deftly moves this extended and skinny beak to pluck prey.
fearow.name: fearow

feebas.dex_entry: Feebas live in ponds that are heavily infested with weeds. Because of its hopelessly shabby appearance, it seems as if few trainers raise it.
feebas.name: feebas

fennekin.dex_entry: As it walks, it munches on a twig in place of a snack. It intimidates opponents by puffing hot air out of its ears.
fennekin.name: fennekin

feraligatr.dex_entry: It opens its huge mouth to intimidate enemies. In battle, it runs using its thick and powerful hind legs to charge the foe with incredible speed.
feraligatr.name: feraligatr

ferroseed.dex_entry: They stick their spikes into cave walls and absorb the minerals they find in the rock.
ferroseed.name: ferroseed

ferrothorn.dex_entry: They attach themselves to cave ceilings, firing steel spikes at targets passing beneath them.
ferrothorn.name: ferrothorn

finneon.dex_entry: After long exposure to sunlight, the patterns on its tail fins shine vividly when darkness arrives.
finneon.name: finneon

flaaffy.dex_entry: Its fleece quality changes to generate strong static electricity with a small amount of wool. The bare, slick parts of its hide are shielded against electricity.
flaaffy.name: flaaffy

flabebe.dex_entry: When it finds a flower it likes, it dwells on that flower its whole life long. It floats in the windΓÇÖs embrace with an untroubled heart.
flabebe.name: flabebe

flareon.dex_entry: Flareon's fluffy fur releases heat into the air so that its body does not get excessively hot. Its body temperature can rise to a maximum of 1,650 degrees F.
flareon.name: flareon

fletchinder.dex_entry: The hotter the flame sac on its belly, the faster it can fly, but it takes some time to get the fire going.
fletchinder.name: fletchinder

fletchling.dex_entry: These friendly Pokemon send signals to one another with beautiful chirps and tail-feather movements.
fletchling.name: fletchling

floatzel.dex_entry: It floats using its well-developed flotation sac. It assists in the rescues of drowning people.
floatzel.name: floatzel

floette.dex_entry: It flutters around fields of flowers and cares for flowers that are starting to wilt. It draws out the power of flowers to battle.
floette.name: floette

florges.dex_entry: It claims exquisite flower gardens as its territory, and it obtains power from basking in the energy emitted by flowering plants.
florges.name: florges

flygon.dex_entry: The flapping of its wings sounds like singing. To prevent detection by enemies, it hides itself by flapping up a cloud of desert sand.
flygon.name: flygon

fomantis.dex_entry: During the day, it sleeps and soaks up light. When night falls, it walks around looking for a safer place to sleep.
fomantis.name: fomantis

foongus.dex_entry: For some reason, this Pokémon resembles a Poké Ball. They release poison spores to repel those who try to catch them.
foongus.name: foongus

forretress.dex_entry: It keeps itself inside its steel shell. The shell is opened when it is catching prey, but it is so quick that the shell's inside cannot be seen.
forretress.name: forretress

fraxure.dex_entry: Their tusks can shatter rocks. Territory battles between Fraxure can be intensely violent.
fraxure.name: fraxure

frillish.dex_entry: They paralyze prey with poison, then drag them down to their lairs, five miles below the surface.
frillish.name: frillish

froakie.dex_entry: It protects its skin by covering its body in delicate bubbles. Beneath its happy-go-lucky air, it keeps a watchful eye on its surroundings.
froakie.name: froakie

frogadier.dex_entry: It can throw bubble-covered pebbles with precise control, hitting empty cans up to a hundred feet away.
frogadier.name: frogadier

froslass.dex_entry: It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees F. What seems to be its body is actually hollow.
froslass.name: froslass

furfrou.dex_entry: Historically, in the Kalos region, these Pokemon were the designated guardians of the king.
furfrou.name: furfrou

furret.dex_entry: A Furret has a very slim build. When under attack, it can squirm through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, it is very nimble and fleet.
furret.name: furret

gabite.dex_entry: There is a long-held belief that medicine made from its scales will heal even incurable illnesses.
gabite.name: gabite

gallade.dex_entry: A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows.
gallade.name: gallade

galvantula.dex_entry: They employ an electrically charged web to trap their prey. While it is immobilized by shock, they leisurely consume it.
galvantula.name: galvantula

garbodor.dex_entry: They absorb garbage and make it part of their bodies. They shoot a poisonous liquid from their right-hand fingertips.
garbodor.name: garbodor

garchomp.dex_entry: When it folds up its body and extends its wings, it looks like a jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.
garchomp.name: garchomp

gardevoir.dex_entry: It apparently does not feel the pull of gravity because it supports itself with psychic power. It will give its life to protect its trainer.
gardevoir.name: gardevoir

gastly.dex_entry: When exposed to a strong wind, a Gastly's gaseous body quickly dwindles away. They cluster under the eaves of houses to escape the ravages of wind.
gastly.name: gastly

gastrodon.dex_entry: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it grows right back.
gastrodon.name: gastrodon

genesect.dex_entry: This ancient bug Pokémon was altered by Team Plasma. They upgraded the cannon on its back.
genesect.name: genesect

gengar.dex_entry: Deep in the night, your shadow cast by a streetlight may suddenly overtake you. It is actually a Gengar running past you, pretending to be your shadow.
gengar.name: gengar

geodude.dex_entry: It climbs mountain paths using only the power of its arms. Because they look just like boulders lining paths, hikers may step on them without noticing.
geodude.name: geodude

geodude-alola.dex_entry: Its body is a magnetic stone. Iron sand attaches to the portions of its body that are particularly magnetic.
geodude-alola.name: geodude-alola

gible.dex_entry: It nests in small, horizontal holes in cave walls. It pounces to catch prey that stray too close.
gible.name: gible

gigalith.dex_entry: The solar energy absorbed by its body's orange crystals is magnified internally and fired from its mouth.
gigalith.name: gigalith

girafarig.dex_entry: A Girafarig is an herbivore--it eats grass and tree shoots. While it is eating, its tail makes chewing and swallowing motions as if it were also eating.
girafarig.name: girafarig

giratina.dex_entry: A Pokémon that is said to live in a world on the reverse side of ours. It appears in an ancient cemetery.
giratina.name: giratina

glaceon.dex_entry: As a protective technique, it can completely freeze its fur to make its hairs stand like needles.
glaceon.name: glaceon

glalie.dex_entry: A Glalie has the power to instantaneously freeze moisture in the atmosphere. A dazzling cloud of diamondlike ice crystals forms around its body.
glalie.name: glalie

glameow.dex_entry: It claws if displeased and purrs when affectionate. Its fickleness is very popular among some.
glameow.name: glameow

gligar.dex_entry: It glides without making a single sound. It grasps the face of its foe using its hind and large front claws, then stabs with its poison barb.
gligar.name: gligar

gliscor.dex_entry: It observes prey while hanging inverted from branches. When the chance presents itself, it swoops!
gliscor.name: gliscor

gloom.dex_entry: A horribly noxious honey drools from its mouth. One whiff of the honey can result in memory loss. Some fans are said to enjoy this overwhelming stink, however.
gloom.name: gloom

gogoat.dex_entry: They inhabit mountainous regions. The leader of the herd is decided by a battle of clashing horns.
gogoat.name: gogoat

golbat.dex_entry: Its fangs easily puncture even thick animal hide. It loves to feast on the blood of people and Pokémon. It flits about in darkness and strikes from behind.
golbat.name: golbat

goldeen.dex_entry: In the springtime, schools of Goldeen can be seen swimming up falls and rivers. It metes out staggering damage with its single horn.
goldeen.name: goldeen

golduck.dex_entry: A Golduck is an adept swimmer. It sometimes joins competitive swimmers in training. It uses psychic powers when its forehead shimmers with light.
golduck.name: golduck

golem.dex_entry: It is said to live in volcanic craters on mountain peaks. Once a year, it sheds its hide and grows larger. The shed hide crumbles and returns to the soil.
golem.name: golem

golem-alola.dex_entry: Because it can't fire boulders at a rapid pace, it's been known to seize nearby Geodude and fire them from its back.
golem-alola.name: golem-alola

golett.dex_entry: These Pokémon are thought to have been created by the science of an ancient and mysterious civilization.
golett.name: golett

golisopod.dex_entry: With a flashing slash of its giant sharp claws, it cleaves seawater - or even air - right into two.
golisopod.name: golisopod

golurk.dex_entry: It is said that Golurk were ordered to protect people and Pokémon by the ancient people who made them.
golurk.name: golurk

goodra.dex_entry: This very friendly Dragon-type Pokemon will hug its beloved Trainer, leaving that Trainer covered in sticky slime.
goodra.name: goodra

goomy.dex_entry: The weakest Dragon-type Pokémon, it lives in damp, shady places, so its body doesn't dry out.
goomy.name: goomy

gorebyss.dex_entry: A Gorebyss siphons the body fluids of prey through its thin, tubular mouth. Its light pink body color turns vivid when it finishes feeding.
gorebyss.name: gorebyss

gothita.dex_entry: They intently observe both Trainers and Pokémon. Apparently, they are looking at something that only Gothita can see.
gothita.name: gothita

gothitelle.dex_entry: They can predict the future from the placement and movement of the stars. They can see Trainers' life spans.
gothitelle.name: gothitelle

gothorita.dex_entry: Starlight is the source of their power. At night, they mark star positions by using psychic power to float stones.
gothorita.name: gothorita

gourgeist.dex_entry: It enwraps its prey in its hairlike arms. It sings joyfully as it observes the suffering of its prey.
gourgeist.name: gourgeist

granbull.dex_entry: It has a particularly well-developed lower jaw. The huge fangs are heavy, causing it to tilt its head. Unless it is startled, it will not try to bite.
granbull.name: granbull

graveler.dex_entry: They descend from mountains by tumbling down steep slopes. They are so brutal, they smash aside obstructing trees and massive boulders with thunderous tackles.
graveler.name: graveler

graveler-alola.dex_entry: Its preferred food is dravite. After it's eaten, crystals form inside the Pokémon, rising to the surface of its body.
graveler-alola.name: graveler-alola

greninja.dex_entry: It appears and vanishes with a ninjaΓÇÖs grace. It toys with its enemies using swift movements, while slicing them with throwing stars of sharpest water.
greninja.name: greninja

grimer.dex_entry: Born from polluted sludge in the sea, Grimer's favorite food is anything filthy. They feed on wastewater pumped out from factories.
grimer.name: grimer

grimer-alola.dex_entry: The crystals on Grimer's body are lumps of toxins. If one falls off, lethal poisons leak out.
grimer-alola.name: grimer-alola

grotle.dex_entry: It lives along water in forests. In the daytime, it leaves the forest to sunbathe its treed shell.
grotle.name: grotle

groudon.dex_entry: Groudon has appeared in mythology as the creator of the land. It sleeps in magma underground and is said to make volcanoes erupt on awakening.
groudon.name: groudon

grovyle.dex_entry: Leaves grow out of this Pokémon's body. They help obscure a Grovyle from the eyes of its enemies while it is in a thickly overgrown forest.
grovyle.name: grovyle

growlithe.dex_entry: Its superb sense of smell ensures that this Pokémon won't forget any scent, no matter what. It uses its sense of smell to detect the emotions of others.
growlithe.name: growlithe

grubbin.dex_entry: Its strong jaw enables it to scrape trees and slurp out the sap. It normally lives underground.
grubbin.name: grubbin

grumpig.dex_entry: It stores power in the black pearls on its forehead. When it uses psychic power, it performs an odd dance step. Its style of dancing became hugely popular overseas.
grumpig.name: grumpig

gulpin.dex_entry: This Pokémon's stomach fluid can even digest scrap iron. In one gulp, it can swallow something that is as large as itself.
gulpin.name: gulpin

gumshoos.dex_entry: When it finds a trace of its prey, it patiently stakes out the location, but it's always snoozing by nightfall.
gumshoos.name: gumshoos

gurdurr.dex_entry: They strengthen their bodies by carrying steel beams. They show off their big muscles to their friends.
gurdurr.name: gurdurr

guzzlord.dex_entry: People claim to have seen it gobble mountains and swallow whole building. It is an Ultra Beast.
guzzlord.name: guzzlord

gyarados.dex_entry: It is an extremely vicious and violent Pokémon. When humans begin to fight, it will appear and burn everything to the ground with intensely hot flames.
gyarados.name: gyarados

hakamo-o.dex_entry: It leaps at its prey with a courageous shout. Its scaly punches can tear its opponents to shreds.
hakamo-o.name: hakamo-o

happiny.dex_entry: It loves round white things. It carries an egg-shaped rock in imitation of Chansey.
happiny.name: happiny

hariyama.dex_entry: It has the habit of challenging others without hesitation to tests of strength. It's been known to stand on train tracks and stop trains using forearm thrusts.
hariyama.name: hariyama

haunter.dex_entry: If a Haunter beckons you while it is floating in darkness, don't approach it. This Pokémon will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away.
haunter.name: haunter

hawlucha.dex_entry: Although its body is small, its proficient fighting skills enable it to keep up with big bruisers like Machamp and Hariyama.
hawlucha.name: hawlucha

haxorus.dex_entry: Their sturdy tusks will stay sharp even if used to cut steel beams. These Pokémon are covered in hard armor.
haxorus.name: haxorus

heatmor.dex_entry: Using their very hot, flame-covered tongues, they burn through Durant's steel bodies and consume their insides.
heatmor.name: heatmor

heatran.dex_entry: It dwells in volcanic caves. It digs in with its cross-shaped feet to crawl on ceilings and walls.
heatran.name: heatran

heliolisk.dex_entry: They flare their frills and generate energy. A single Heliolisk can generate sufficiant electricity to power a skyscraper.
heliolisk.name: heliolisk

helioptile.dex_entry: They make their home in desserts. They can generate their energy from basking in the sun, so eating food is not a requirement.
helioptile.name: helioptile

heracross.dex_entry: They gather in forests seeking the sweet sap of trees. It is completely clad in a steel-hard shell. It is proud of its horn, which it uses to fling foes.
heracross.name: heracross

herdier.dex_entry: It loyally follows its Trainer's orders. For ages, they have helped Trainers raise Pokémon.
herdier.name: herdier

hippopotas.dex_entry: It lives in arid places. Instead of perspiration, it expels grainy sand from its body.
hippopotas.name: hippopotas

hippowdon.dex_entry: It blasts internally stored sand from ports on its body to create a towering twister for attack.
hippowdon.name: hippowdon

hitmonchan.dex_entry: A Hitmonchan is said to possess the spirit of a boxer who aimed to become the world champion. Having an indomitable spirit means that it will never give up.
hitmonchan.name: hitmonchan

hitmonlee.dex_entry: Its legs freely stretch and contract. Using these springlike limbs, it bowls over foes with devastating kicks. After battle, it rubs down its tired legs.
hitmonlee.name: hitmonlee

hitmontop.dex_entry: Its technique of kicking while spinning is a remarkable mix of both offense and defense. Hitmontop travel faster spinning than they do walking.
hitmontop.name: hitmontop

honchkrow.dex_entry: Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous Murkrow in tow.
honchkrow.name: honchkrow

honedge.dex_entry: Apparently this Pokemon is born when a departed spirit inhabits a sword. It attaches itself to people and drinks their life force.
honedge.name: honedge

ho-oh.dex_entry: Its feathers--which glow in seven colors depending on the angle at which they are struck by light--are thought to bring joy. It is said to live at the foot of a rainbow.
ho-oh.name: ho-oh

hoopa.dex_entry: It gathers things it likes and pushes them through its loop to teleport them to a secret place.
hoopa.name: hoopa

hoothoot.dex_entry: It has an internal organ that senses the earth's rotation. Using this special organ, a Hoothoot begins hooting at precisely the same time every day.
hoothoot.name: hoothoot

hoppip.dex_entry: This Pokémon drifts and floats with the wind. If it senses the approach of strong winds, a Hoppip links leaves with others to prepare against being blown away.
hoppip.name: hoppip

horsea.dex_entry: By cleverly flicking the fins on its back side to side, it moves in any direction while facing forward. It spits ink to escape if it senses danger.
horsea.name: horsea

houndoom.dex_entry: In a Houndoom pack, the one with its horns raked sharply back serves a leadership role. They choose their leader by fighting among themselves.
houndoom.name: houndoom

houndour.dex_entry: Houndour communicate with each other using a variety of cries to corner their prey. This Pokémon's remarkable teamwork is simply unparalleled.
houndour.name: houndour

huntail.dex_entry: To withstand the crushing pressure of water deep under the sea, its spine is very thick and sturdy. Its tail, which is shaped like a small fish, has eyes that light up.
huntail.name: huntail

hydreigon.dex_entry: The heads on their arms do not have brains. They use all three heads to consume and destroy everything.
hydreigon.name: hydreigon

hypno.dex_entry: The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum in a Hypno's hand lull the foe into deep hypnosis. While searching for prey, it polishes the pendulum.
hypno.name: hypno

igglybuff.dex_entry: Its soft and pliable body is very bouncy. When it sings continuously with all its might, its body steadily turns a deepening pink color.
igglybuff.name: igglybuff

illumise.dex_entry: A nocturnal Pokémon that becomes active upon nightfall. It leads a Volbeat swarm to draw patterns in the night sky. Over 200 different patterns have been confirmed.
illumise.name: illumise

incineroar.dex_entry: This Pokémon has a violent, selfish disposition. When in a bad mood, it may ignore its Trainer's orders with complete nonchalance.
incineroar.name: incineroar

infernape.dex_entry: It uses a special kind of martial arts involving all its limbs. Its fire never goes out.
infernape.name: infernape

inkay.dex_entry: It flashes the light-emitting spots on its body, which drains its opponentΓÇÖs will to fight. It takes the opportunity to scuttle away and hide.
inkay.name: inkay

ivysaur.dex_entry: To support its bulb, Ivysaur's legs grow sturdy. If it spends more time lying in the sunlight, the bud will soon bloom into a large flower.
ivysaur.name: ivysaur

jangmo-o.dex_entry: It expresses its feelings by smacking its scales. Metallic sounds echo through the tall mountains where it lives.
jangmo-o.name: jangmo-o

jellicent.dex_entry: They propel themselves by expelling absorbed seawater from their bodies. Their favorite food is life energy.
jellicent.name: jellicent

jigglypuff.dex_entry: Nothing can avoid falling asleep hearing a Jigglypuff's song. The sound waves of its singing voice match the brain waves of someone in a deep sleep.
jigglypuff.name: jigglypuff

jirachi.dex_entry: Jirachi is said to make wishes come true. While it sleeps, a tough crystalline shell envelops the body to protect it from enemies.
jirachi.name: jirachi

jolteon.dex_entry: Its cells generate weak power that is amplified by its fur's static electricity to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles.
jolteon.name: jolteon

joltik.dex_entry: They attach themselves to large-bodied Pokémon and absorb static electricity, which they store in an electric pouch.
joltik.name: joltik

jumpluff.dex_entry: Jumpluff ride warm southern winds to cross the sea and fly to foreign lands. This Pokémon lands when it encounters cold air while it is floating.
jumpluff.name: jumpluff

jynx.dex_entry: A Jynx sashays rhythmically as if it were dancing. Its motions are so bouncingly alluring, people seeing it are compelled to shake their hips without noticing.
jynx.name: jynx

kabuto.dex_entry: It is a Pokémon that has been regenerated from a fossil. However, in rare cases, living examples have been discovered. Kabuto have not changed for 300 million years.
kabuto.name: kabuto

kabutops.dex_entry: Kabutops once swam underwater to hunt for prey. It was apparently evolving from being a water dweller to living on land as evident from changes in its gills and legs.
kabutops.name: kabutops

kadabra.dex_entry: It is rumored that a boy with psychic abilities suddenly transformed into Kadabra while he was assisting research into extrasensory powers.
kadabra.name: kadabra

kakuna.dex_entry: It remains virtually immobile while it clings to a tree. However, on the inside, it busily prepares for evolution. This is evident from how hot its shell becomes.
kakuna.name: kakuna

kangaskhan.dex_entry: If you come across a young Kangaskhan playing by itself, never try to catch it. The baby's parent is sure to be in the area, and it will become violently enraged.
kangaskhan.name: kangaskhan

karrablast.dex_entry: When they feel threatened, they spit an acidic liquid to drive attackers away. This Pokémon targets Shelmet.
karrablast.name: karrablast

kartana.dex_entry: People observed it cutting down a gigantic steel tower with one stroke of its blade. It is an Ultra Beast.
kartana.name: kartana

kecleon.dex_entry: A Pokémon that has the ability to alter its body colors to match its surroundings. A Kecleon reverts to its original colors if it is startled.
kecleon.name: kecleon

keldeo.dex_entry: It crosses the world, running over the surfaces of oceans and rivers. It appears at scenic waterfronts.
keldeo.name: keldeo

kingdra.dex_entry: It sleeps quietly, deep on the seafloor. When it comes up to the surface, it creates a huge whirlpool that can swallow even ships.
kingdra.name: kingdra

kingler.dex_entry: It waves its huge, oversized claw in the air to communicate with others. But since the claw is so heavy, this Pokémon quickly tires.
kingler.name: kingler

kirlia.dex_entry: A Kirlia has the psychic power to create a rip in the dimensions and see into the future. It is said to dance with pleasure on sunny mornings.
kirlia.name: kirlia

klang.dex_entry: Spinning minigears are rotated at high speed and repeatedly fired away. It is dangerous if the gears don't return.
klang.name: klang

klefki.dex_entry: It never lets go of a key that it likes, so people give it the keys to vaults and safes as a way to prevent crime.
klefki.name: klefki

klink.dex_entry: Interlocking two bodies and spinning around generates the energy they need to live.
klink.name: klink

klinklang.dex_entry: The gear with the red core is rotated at high speed for a rapid energy charge.
klinklang.name: klinklang

koffing.dex_entry: Getting up close to a Koffing will give you a chance to observe, through its thin skin, the toxic gases swirling inside. It blows up at the slightest stimulation.
koffing.name: koffing

komala.dex_entry: The log it holds was give to it by its parents. It is also known to cling to the arm of a friendly Trainer.
komala.name: komala

kommo-o.dex_entry: When it spots enemies, it threatens them by jingling its scales. Weak opponents will crack and flee in panic.
kommo-o.name: kommo-o

krabby.dex_entry: Krabby live in holes dug into beaches. On sandy shores with little in the way of food, they can be seen squabbling with each other over territory.
krabby.name: krabby

kricketot.dex_entry: It shakes its head back to front, causing its antennae to hit each other and sound like a xylophone.
kricketot.name: kricketot

kricketune.dex_entry: It crosses its knifelike arms in front of its chest when it cries. It can compose melodies ad lib.
kricketune.name: kricketune

krokorok.dex_entry: The special membrane covering its eyes can sense the heat of objects, so it can see its surroundings, even in darkness.
krokorok.name: krokorok

krookodile.dex_entry: It can expand the focus of its eyes, enabling it to see objects in the far distance as if it were using binoculars.
krookodile.name: krookodile

kyogre.dex_entry: Kyogre has appeared in mythology as the creator of the sea. After long years of feuding with Groudon, it took to sleep at the bottom of the sea.
kyogre.name: kyogre

kyurem.dex_entry: It generates a powerful, freezing energy inside itself, but its body became frozen when the energy leaked out.
kyurem.name: kyurem

lairon.dex_entry: When two Lairon meet in the wild, they fight for territory by bashing into each other with their steel bodies. The sound of their collision carries for miles.
lairon.name: lairon

lampent.dex_entry: It arrives near the moment of death and steals spirit from the body.
lampent.name: lampent

landorus.dex_entry: The energy that comes pouring from its tail increases the nutrition in the soil, making crops grow to great size.
landorus.name: landorus

lanturn.dex_entry: The light-emitting orbs on its back are very bright. They are formed from a part of its dorsal fin. This Pokémon illuminates the inky darkness of deep seas.
lanturn.name: lanturn

lapras.dex_entry: People have driven Lapras almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, it is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain.
lapras.name: lapras

larvesta.dex_entry: The base of volcanoes is where they make their homes. They shoot fire from their five horns to repel attacking enemies.
larvesta.name: larvesta

larvitar.dex_entry: A Larvitar is born deep under the ground. It must eat its way through the soil above and reach the surface for it to see its parents' faces.
larvitar.name: larvitar

latias.dex_entry: They make a small herd of only several members. They rarely make contact with people or other Pokémon. They disappear if they sense enemies.
latias.name: latias

latios.dex_entry: Even in hiding, it can detect the locations of others and sense their emotions since it has telepathy. Its intelligence allows it to understand human languages.
latios.name: latios

leafeon.dex_entry: Just like a plant, it uses photosynthesis. As a result, it is always enveloped in clear air.
leafeon.name: leafeon

leavanny.dex_entry: It keeps its eggs warm with heat from fermenting leaves. It also uses leaves to make warm wrappings for Sewaddle.
leavanny.name: leavanny

ledian.dex_entry: It is said that in lands with clean air, where the stars fill the sky, there live many Ledian. For good reason, they use the light of the stars as energy.
ledian.name: ledian

ledyba.dex_entry: Ledyba communicate using a fluid that they secrete from where the legs join the body. They are said to convey feelings to others by altering the fluid's scent.
ledyba.name: ledyba

lickilicky.dex_entry: It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool.
lickilicky.name: lickilicky

lickitung.dex_entry: Whenever it sees something unfamiliar, it always licks the object because it memorizes things by texture and taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things.
lickitung.name: lickitung

liepard.dex_entry: Stealthily, it sneaks up on its target, striking from behind before its victim has a chance to react.
liepard.name: liepard

lileep.dex_entry: It disguises itself as seaweed by making its tentacles sway. Unsuspecting prey that come too close are swallowed whole. It became extinct 100 million years ago.
lileep.name: lileep

lilligant.dex_entry: The fragrance of the garland on its head has a relaxing effect. It withers if a Trainer does not take good care of it.
lilligant.name: lilligant

lillipup.dex_entry: The long hair around its face provides an amazing radar that lets it sense subtle changes in its surroundings.
lillipup.name: lillipup

linoone.dex_entry: It is exceedingly fast if it only has to run in a straight line. When it spots pond- dwelling prey underwater, it quickly leaps in and catches it with its sharp claws.
linoone.name: linoone

litleo.dex_entry: They set off on their own from their pride and live by themselves to become stronger. These hot-blooded Pokémon are quick to fight.
litleo.name: litleo

litten.dex_entry: While grooming itself, it build up fur inside its stomach. It sets the fur alight and spews fiery attacks, which change based on how it coughs.
litten.name: litten

litwick.dex_entry: While shining a light and pretending to be a guide, it leeches off the life force of any who follow it.
litwick.name: litwick

lombre.dex_entry: In the evening, it takes great delight in popping out of rivers and startling people. It feeds on aquatic moss that grows on rocks in the riverbed.
lombre.name: lombre

lopunny.dex_entry: An extremely cautious Pokémon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.
lopunny.name: lopunny

lotad.dex_entry: This Pokémon lives in ponds with clean water. It is known to ferry small Pokémon across ponds by carrying them on the broad leaf on its head.
lotad.name: lotad

loudred.dex_entry: It positions the round speakers on its head to assail foes with ultrasonic waves at massive volume. It builds power by stomping the ground.
loudred.name: loudred

lucario.dex_entry: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.
lucario.name: lucario

ludicolo.dex_entry: When it hears festive music, all the cells in its body become stimulated, and it begins moving in rhythm. It does not quail even when it faces a tough opponent.
ludicolo.name: ludicolo

lugia.dex_entry: Lugia is so powerful even a light fluttering of its wings can blow apart houses. As a result, it chooses to live out of sight deep under the sea.
lugia.name: lugia

lumineon.dex_entry: It lives on the deep-sea floor. It attracts prey by flashing the patterns on its four tail fins.
lumineon.name: lumineon

lunala.dex_entry: When its third eye activates, away it flies to another world where it is said to live.
lunala.name: lunala

lunatone.dex_entry: It becomes very active on the night of a full moon. This Pokémon was first discovered 40 years ago at the site of a meteor strike.
lunatone.name: lunatone

lurantis.dex_entry: It fires beams from its petals. These beams are powerful enough to cleave through thick metal plates.
lurantis.name: lurantis

luvdisc.dex_entry: Luvdisc make the branches of Corsola their nests. There is a custom from long ago of giving a Luvdisc as a gift to express one's feelings of love.
luvdisc.name: luvdisc

luxio.dex_entry: Its claws loose electricity with enough amperage to cause fainting. They live in small groups.
luxio.name: luxio

luxray.dex_entry: It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.
luxray.name: luxray

lycanroc.dex_entry: Its quick moves confuse its enemies. Well equipped with claws and fangs, it also uses the rocks in its mane as weapons.
lycanroc.name: lycanroc

machamp.dex_entry: It is impossible to defend against punches and chops doled out by its four arms. Its fighting spirit flares up when it faces a tough opponent.
machamp.name: machamp

machoke.dex_entry: A belt is worn by a Machoke to keep its overwhelming power under control. Because it is so dangerous, no one has ever removed the belt.
machoke.name: machoke

machop.dex_entry: It continually undertakes strenuous training to master all forms of martial arts. Its strength lets it easily hoist a sumo wrestler onto its shoulders.
machop.name: machop

magby.dex_entry: If a Magby is spouting yellow flames from its mouth, it is in good health. When it is fatigued, black smoke will be mixed in with the flames.
magby.name: magby

magcargo.dex_entry: The shell on its back is made of hardened magma. Tens of thousands of years spent living in volcanic craters have turned Magcargo's bodies into magma.
magcargo.name: magcargo

magearna.dex_entry: This artificial Pokémon, more than 500 years old, can understand human speech but cannot speak itself.
magearna.name: magearna

magikarp.dex_entry: Its swimming muscles are weak, so it is easily washed away by currents. In places where water pools, you can see many Magikarp deposited there by the flow.
magikarp.name: magikarp

magmar.dex_entry: In battle, it blows out intense flames from all over its body to intimidate its foe. These fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in the area.
magmar.name: magmar

magmortar.dex_entry: It blasts fireballs of over 3,600 degrees F from the ends of its arms. It lives in volcanic craters.
magmortar.name: magmortar

magnemite.dex_entry: The units at its sides are extremely powerful magnets. They generate enough magnetism to draw in iron objects from over 300 feet away.
magnemite.name: magnemite

magneton.dex_entry: It is actually three Magnemite linked by magnetism. It generates powerful radio waves that raise temperatures by 3.6 degrees F within a 3,300-foot radius.
magneton.name: magneton

magnezone.dex_entry: It evolved from exposure to a special magnetic field. Three units generate magnetism.
magnezone.name: magnezone

makuhita.dex_entry: It loves to toughen up its body above all else. If you hear quaking rumbles in a cave, it is the sound of Makuhita undertaking strenuous training.
makuhita.name: makuhita

malamar.dex_entry: It lures its prey close with hypnotic motions, then wraps its tentacles around it before finishing it off with digestive fluids.
malamar.name: malamar

mamoswine.dex_entry: Its impressive tusks are made of ice. The population thinned when it turned warm after the ice age.
mamoswine.name: mamoswine

manaphy.dex_entry: Born on a cold seafloor, it will swim great distances to return to its birthplace.
manaphy.name: manaphy

mandibuzz.dex_entry: Watching from the sky, they swoop to strike weakened Pokémon on the ground. They decorate themselves with bones.
mandibuzz.name: mandibuzz

manectric.dex_entry: Because lightning falls in their vicinities, Manectric were thought to have been born from lightning. In battle, they create thunderclouds.
manectric.name: manectric

mankey.dex_entry: When it starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns rough, it's a sure sign of anger. However, since this happens instantly, there is no time to flee.
mankey.name: mankey

mantine.dex_entry: On sunny days, schools of Mantine can be seen elegantly leaping over the waves. It is not bothered by the Remoraid that hitches rides.
mantine.name: mantine

mantyke.dex_entry: A friendly Pokémon that captures the subtle flows of seawater using its two antennae.
mantyke.name: mantyke

maractus.dex_entry: Arid regions are their habitat. They move rhythmically, making a sound similar to maracas.
maractus.name: maractus

mareanie.dex_entry: The coral that grows on Corsola's head is as good as a five-star banquet to this Pokémon.
mareanie.name: mareanie

mareep.dex_entry: Its fluffy wool rubs together and builds a static charge. The more energy is charged, the more brightly the lightbulb at the tip of its tail glows.
mareep.name: mareep

marill.dex_entry: Its body is covered with water-repellent fur. Because of the fur, it can swim through water at high speed without being slowed by the water's resistance.
marill.name: marill

marowak.dex_entry: A Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has grown tough by overcoming the grief of losing its mother. Its tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.
marowak.name: marowak

marowak-alola.dex_entry: Its custom is to mourn its lost companions. Mounds of dirt by the side of the road mark the graves of the Marowak.
marowak-alola.name: marowak-alola

marshadow.dex_entry: Able to conceal itself in shadows, it never appears before human, so its very existence was the stuff of myth.
marshadow.name: marshadow

marshtomp.dex_entry: Its toughened hind legs enable it to stand upright. Because it weakens if its skin dries out, it replenishes fluids by playing in mud.
marshtomp.name: marshtomp

masquerain.dex_entry: It intimidates foes with the large eyelike patterns on its antennae. Because it can't fly if its wings get wet, it shelters itself from rain under large trees and eaves.
masquerain.name: masquerain

mawile.dex_entry: Its giant jaws are actually steel horns that transformed. It fools foes into complacency with its adorable gestures, then chomps them with its huge jaws.
mawile.name: mawile

medicham.dex_entry: Through crushingly harsh yoga training, it gained the power to foretell its foe's actions. It battles with elegant, dance- like movement.
medicham.name: medicham

meditite.dex_entry: It continually meditates for hours every day. As a result of rigorous and dedicated yoga training, it has tempered its spiritual power so much it can fly.
meditite.name: meditite

meganium.dex_entry: The fragrance of a Meganium's flower soothes and calms emotions. In battle, it gives off more of its becalming scent to blunt the foe's fighting spirit.
meganium.name: meganium

meloetta.dex_entry: Many famous songs have been inspired by the melodies that Meloetta plays.
meloetta.name: meloetta

meowstic.dex_entry: When in danger, it raises its ears and releases enough psychic power to grind a 10-ton truck to dust.
meowstic.name: meowstic

meowth.dex_entry: Meowth withdraw their sharp claws into their paws to silently sneak about. For some reason, this Pokémon loves shiny coins that glitter with light.
meowth.name: meowth

meowth-alola.dex_entry: When its pride is wounded, or when the gold coin on its forehead is dirtied, it flies into a hysterical rage.
meowth-alola.name: meowth-alola

mesprit.dex_entry: Known as ΓÇ£The Being of Emotion.ΓÇ¥ It taught humans the nobility of sorrow, pain, and joy.
mesprit.name: mesprit

metagross.dex_entry: Metagross has four brains that are joined by a complex neural network. As a result of integration, this Pokémon is smarter than a supercomputer.
metagross.name: metagross

metang.dex_entry: The claws tipping its arms pack the destructive power to tear through thick iron sheets as if they were silk. It flies at over 60 miles per hour.
metang.name: metang

metapod.dex_entry: Its shell is as hard as an iron slab. A Metapod does not move very much because it is preparing its soft innards for evolution inside the shell.
metapod.name: metapod

mew.dex_entry: A Mew is said to possess the genes of all Pokémon. It is capable of making itself invisible at will, so it entirely avoids notice even if it approaches people.
mew.name: mew

mewtwo.dex_entry: A Pokémon that was created by genetic manipulation. However, even though the scientific power of humans made its body, they failed to give it a warm heart.
mewtwo.name: mewtwo

mienfoo.dex_entry: They have mastered elegant combos. As they concentrate, their battle moves become swifter and more precise.
mienfoo.name: mienfoo

mienshao.dex_entry: They use the long fur on their arms as a whip to strike their opponents.
mienshao.name: mienshao

mightyena.dex_entry: In the wild, Mightyena live in a pack. They never defy their leader's orders. They defeat foes with perfectly coordinated teamwork.
mightyena.name: mightyena

milotic.dex_entry: It is said to live at the bottom of large lakes. Considered to be the most beautiful of all Pokémon, it has been depicted in paintings and statues.
milotic.name: milotic

miltank.dex_entry: It gives over five gallons of milk daily. Its sweet milk is enjoyed by children and grown-ups alike. People who can't drink milk turn it into yogurt and eat it instead.
miltank.name: miltank

mime-jr.dex_entry: It habitually mimics foes. Once mimicked, the foe cannot take its eyes off this Pokémon.
mime-jr.name: mime-jr

mimikyu.dex_entry: Its actual appearance is unknown. When a scholar saw what was under its rag, it was overwhelmed by terror and died.
mimikyu.name: mimikyu

minccino.dex_entry: These Pokémon prefer a tidy habitat. They are always sweeping and dusting, using their tails as brooms.
minccino.name: minccino

minior.dex_entry: Strong impacts can knock it out of its shell. This Pokémon was born from mutated nanoparticles.
minior.name: minior

minun.dex_entry: At a meeting of Pokémon academics, it was announced that simultaneous exposure to electricity from a Plusle and Minun will promote circulation and boost vitality.
minun.name: minun

misdreavus.dex_entry: A Misdreavus frightens people with a creepy, sobbing cry. It apparently uses its red spheres to absorb the fear of foes as its nutrition.
misdreavus.name: misdreavus

mismagius.dex_entry: Its cries sound like incantations. Those hearing it are tormented by headaches and hallucinations.
mismagius.name: mismagius

moltres.dex_entry: Moltres is a legendary bird Pokémon that can control fire. If injured, it is said to dip its body in the molten magma of a volcano to burn and heal itself.
moltres.name: moltres

monferno.dex_entry: To intimidate attackers, it stretches the fire on its tail to make itself appear bigger.
monferno.name: monferno

morelull.dex_entry: It scatters spores that flicker and glow. Anyone seeing these lights falls into a deep slumber.
morelull.name: morelull

mothim.dex_entry: It loves the honey of flowers and steals honey collected by Combee.
mothim.name: mothim

mr-mime.dex_entry: A Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. It can convince others that something unseeable actually exists. Once believed, the imaginary object does become real.
mr-mime.name: mr-mime

mudbray.dex_entry: The mud stuck to Mudbray's hooves enhances its grip and its powerful running gait.
mudbray.name: mudbray

mudkip.dex_entry: On land, it can powerfully lift large boulders by planting its four feet and heaving. It sleeps by burying itself in soil at the water's edge.
mudkip.name: mudkip

mudsdale.dex_entry: It spits a mud that provides resistance to both wind and rain, so the walls of old houses were often coated with it.
mudsdale.name: mudsdale

muk.dex_entry: It prefers warm and humid habitats. In the summertime, the toxic substances in its body intensify, making Muk reek like putrid kitchen garbage.
muk.name: muk

muk-alola.dex_entry: The garbage it eats causes continuous chemical changes in its body, which produce its exceedingly vivid coloration.
muk-alola.name: muk-alola

munchlax.dex_entry: It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.
munchlax.name: munchlax

munna.dex_entry: It eats the dreams of people and Pokémon. When it eats a pleasant dreams, it expels pink-colored mist.
munna.name: munna

murkrow.dex_entry: Murkrow were feared as the alleged bearers of ill fortune. It shows strong interest in anything that sparkles. It will even try to steal rings from women.
murkrow.name: murkrow

musharna.dex_entry: With the mist from its forehead, it can create shapes of things from dreams it has eaten.
musharna.name: musharna

natu.dex_entry: It runs up short trees that grow on the savanna to peck at new shoots. A Natu's eyes look as if they are always observing something.
natu.name: natu

necrozma.dex_entry: Light is apparently the source of its energy. It is thought to have come from another world in ancient times.
necrozma.name: necrozma

nidoking.dex_entry: A Nidoking's thick tail packs enormously destructive power capable of toppling a metal transmission tower. Once it goes on a rampage, there is no stopping it.
nidoking.name: nidoking

nidoqueen.dex_entry: It is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles using its tough, scaly body. This Pokémon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.
nidoqueen.name: nidoqueen
